edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database

Class AnimalDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database.AnimalDatabase

  • public class AnimalDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages tables storing animal data. When animals are retrieved, these one can be listed by age (AGE) or by animal identifier (ANIMALID). A future release may sort animals by their parents or other criteria
    Author:
    patricio
